				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Newbie here!<a name="35785"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 21 04 2:06 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The song you're talking about, Cinda's Charismatic Carillon, raises your faction with the target and every NPC in the zone on the same faction.  So if you hit a target that is on, say, Merchants of Kelethin faction, all the merchants now like you better.  However, if something is totally Kill-on-Sight toward you, the faction song won't fix that.</span></td>
