Thanks for the responses! I've read the guides about AE kiting, but I'm not sure I understand how Fear kiting works exactly. I've used Fear twice. Once was when I was playing with it in LIO, I just hit snare, then fear and it couldn't really move or hit me. The second time was a learning experience. I was in Mistmore in the graveyard when our puller brought us several reds, including a pet and temptress. The temptress was killing our only cleric so I feared her. We were already running for the zone when I realized that I'd basically used a strong AE and pulled damnear the ENTIRE castle!! (blush) I told everyone what I did and they thanked me for the screenshots they got. ;)
